    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a Halloween mansion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To escape, follow the rules and take action accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－Rules－</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Proceed if there is nothing unusual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Turn back if you encounter something strange.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Head toward the exit, which is your goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆8th Like's Walking Simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;8ALLOWEEN&quot; is a walking simulator inspired by the 8th exit and other similar concepts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Anomalies that Emit Sound</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies require identification by sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Therefore, it is recommended to use speakers or headphones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆This game contains mild horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The expected playtime is 20 to 60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Video Distribution Guidelines</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Individuals and organizations alike are allowed to upload and stream videos without prior permission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monetization is permitted only when using the features provided by the video distribution platform.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We would appreciate it if you could include the game’s name in the video or stream title, and add a link to the official page or store page in the description.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We bear no responsibility for any damages that may occur as a result of uploading or streaming videos related to this game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These guidelines are subject to change without prior notice.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Please report bugs here.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
